      • setLoadProxy

        public Connect.Builder setLoadProxy(java.lang.String appId,
                                    java.lang.String appKey,
                                    java.lang.String scvProxyUrl,
                                    java.lang.String pfProxyUrl)
        Note that this method will work only for scv. Call this method if your app needs to set up the load proxy. This load proxy will be used to avoid the server down with a high number of requests. The proxy will return an http erroc code once the proxy gets the maximun of calls allowed.
        Parameters:
        appId - String containing the app id used for proxy authentication
        appKey - String containing the key used for proxy authentication
        scvProxyUrl - Url used for the scv proxy.
        pfProxyUrl - Url used for the ping federate proxy.
        Returns:
        Builder to continue building connect client.

      • setLoadProxy

        public Connect.Builder setLoadProxy(java.lang.String scvProxyUrl,
                                    java.lang.String pfProxyUrl)
        Note that this method will work only for scv. Call this method if your app needs to set up the load proxy. This load proxy will be used to avoid the server down with a high number of requests. The proxy will return an http erroc code once the proxy gets the maximun of calls allowed. This method will do an extra call to get a pair of key and app id.
        Parameters:
        scvProxyUrl - The url for the scv proxy
        pfProxyUrl - Thu url for ping federate proxy.
        Returns:
        Builder to continuen building connect client.
